The follwing steps detail how to add a Physical Surface Type to your project.

1. Edit -> Project Settings... -> Physics -> Physical Surface Category
1. Change the "None" in the Name field next to a "SurfaceType#" to a name descriptive of what you'd like the Surface Type to represent (concrete, flesh, wood, etc...)

